# Raw/private customer evidence and extracted source data
*.dwg
*.dxf
*.pdf
*.xls
*.xlsx
*.xlsm
*.xlsb
*.zip
*.7z
*.rar
*.accdb
tmp/
evals/sandboxes/
evals/references/
evals/runs/*/generated/
